name: New Collections Sell Through Report
query: SELECT CONCAT( "" ) as "Image::150", i.description as "Description::250", ld.launch_year_name as "Launch Year::100", ( SELECT SUM(slep.actual_qty) FROM `tabItem` ti LEFT JOIN `tabStock Ledger Entry` slep ON slep.item_code = ti.item_code WHERE ti.variant_of = i.item_code AND slep.actual_qty > 0 ) as "Total Qty::100", ( SELECT ABS( SUM(slen.actual_qty) ) FROM `tabItem` tin LEFT JOIN `tabStock Ledger Entry` slen ON slen.item_code = tin.item_code WHERE tin.variant_of = i.item_code AND slen.actual_qty < 0 ) as "Sales from till date::130", ( ( SELECT ABS( ( SUM(tslen.actual_qty)/ SUM(tslep.actual_qty) )* 100 ) FROM `tabItem` tti LEFT JOIN `tabStock Ledger Entry` tslep ON tslep.item_code = tti.item_code LEFT JOIN `tabStock Ledger Entry` tslen ON tslen.item_code = tti.item_code WHERE tti.variant_of = i.item_code AND tslep.actual_qty > 0 AND tslen.actual_qty < 0 ) ) as "Sell Thru Perc::100", ( SELECT ipa.price_list_rate from `tabItem` ip LEFT JOIN `tabItem Price` ipa ON ip.item_code = ipa.item_code AND ipa.selling = 1 WHERE ip.variant_of = i.item_code LIMIT 1 ) as "MRP::100" FROM `tabItem` i LEFT JOIN `tabLaunch Details` ld ON i.launch_year = ld.name LEFT JOIN `tabItem Price` ip ON ip.item_code = i.item_code AND ip.selling = 1 WHERE i.variant_of IS NULL AND i.has_variants = 1 UNION SELECT CONCAT( "" ) as "Image::150", i.description as "Description::250", ld.launch_year_name as "Launch Year::100", ( SELECT SUM(slep.actual_qty) FROM `tabStock Ledger Entry` slep WHERE slep.item_code = i.item_code AND slep.actual_qty > 0 ) as "Total Qty::100", ( SELECT ABS( SUM(slen.actual_qty) ) FROM `tabStock Ledger Entry` slen WHERE slen.item_code = i.item_code AND slen.actual_qty < 0 ) as "Sales from till date::130", ( SELECT ABS( ( SUM(tslen.actual_qty)/ SUM(tslep.actual_qty) )* 100 ) from `tabStock Ledger Entry` tslep, `tabStock Ledger Entry` tslen WHERE tslep.item_code = i.item_code AND tslep.actual_qty > 0 AND tslen.item_code = i.item_code AND tslen.actual_qty < 0 ) as "Sell Thru Perc::100", ip.price_list_rate as "MRP::100" FROM `tabItem` i LEFT JOIN `tabLaunch Details` ld ON i.launch_year = ld.name LEFT JOIN `tabItem Price` ip ON ip.item_code = i.item_code AND ip.selling = 1 WHERE i.variant_of IS NULL AND i.has_variants = 0

name: Sales Order Item-wise Stock Report
query:
select s.name as "Sales Order:Link/Sales Order",
si.item_name as "Item:Link/Item",
w.name as "Warehouse:Link/Warehouse",
IFNULL(b.actual_qty,0) as "Qty"
from `tabSales Order`s
left join `tabWarehouse`w
on w.name!=""
left join `tabSales Order Item`si
on si.parent=s.name
left join `tabBin` b
on b.item_code=si.item_code and w.name=b.warehouse
order by s.name
